  "summary": "Shane Drohan is a 27-year-old left-handed pitcher recently acquired by the Milwaukee Brewers in a February 2026 trade from the Boston Red Sox. He features a diverse five-pitch arsenal and has shown increased velocity after recovering from nerve decompression surgery in 2024 and dealing with forearm inflammation in 2025. He projects as a potential back-of-the-rotation starter or multi-inning reliever, with questions remaining about his command consistency and durability over a full season.",
